cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to extract relations between named entities from free text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves unsupervised learning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses word embeddings, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves feature reduction, which could suggest it belongs to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
